question: Ashley is required to submit a 258-page report. She already finished writing 1/2 of the report. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Ashley has already written 1/2 of the report which is 258 pages*1/2 = <<258*1/2=129>>129 pages.
So, she still needs to write 258 pages - 129 pages = <<258-129=129>>129 pages.
#### 129
